## A New Post

Most likely, you have already heard the infamous quote from Bill Gates that 'I choose a lazy person to do a hard job. Because a lazy person will find an easy way to do it.' And also noticed about a pletora of research finding evidence about lazy people being smarter. But this post in not about that. Couple of day ago, I had a long walk and plenty of time for talking to myslef :D The discussion (:D) was baout the fact that I really enjoy coding sometimes. Then a question came up,  what kind of coding?

